title: Tell Us How You Really Feel About the Dresses at the People's Choice Awards
text: Best   Dresses 2017 Tell Us How You Really Feel About the Dresses at the   January 18, 2017 by Sarah Wasilak 28 Shares Even more glorious than gazing at the   gowns is offering your opinion about all of them. Which dress would you slip into in an instant, and which would you leave on the rack? Now's your chance to play stylist as you swipe left and right on the celebrity looks of the night. Don't be shy, because this little game is about to become your secret addiction. You're Finished!
